{DIALOGUE}: How'd it go?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARTHUR
{DIALOGUE}: Not good.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Arthur checks the remaining three countdowns, and we-
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
