{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 16.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. BULLET TRAIN COMPARTMENT - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Arthur retracts the tubes into the case as he watches the next countdown hit ZERO, and we-
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. DILAPIDATED HOTEL ROOM - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Another BANG on the door- Saito, confident now, approaches Cobb.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Nash is behind Saito.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAITO
