{DIALOGUE}: Ah, yes, but you see, Mr. Saito-
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Saito turns to Nash-
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: We're not in your dream-
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Saito turns back to Cobb, BUT COBB HAS VANISHED-
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NASH
{DIALOGUE}: We're in mine.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Saito SPINS back to Nash- the DOOR SMASHES OFF ITS HINGES AS RIOTERS POUR INTO THE ROOM, SWARMING OVER NASH... BUT NASH IS GONE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The music DIES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Saito and the rioters stand there in the SILENCE, the light DWINDLING... and we-
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. BULLET TRAIN COMPARTMENT - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Nash' eyes open, AWAKE.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARTHUR (O.S.)
{DIALOGUE}: Asshole!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Nash BLINKS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Arthur is in his face, furious.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARTHUR
