{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Arthur SLAMS the silver case shut.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Todashi pulls open the door-
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: Every man for himself.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Arthur and Nash EXIT, heading in different directions down the corridor.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cobb hands Todashi a thick roll of CASH, looks at Saito, who stirs.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cobb moves off.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. JAPANESE COUNTRYSIDE - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The BULLET TRAIN speeds through the lush landscape.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. BULLET TRAIN COMPARTMENT - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Saito WAKES GENTLY.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Looks around the compartment, empty but for Todashi, reading a comic.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Saito looks down at his wrist.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sees a small mark.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Rubs it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SMILES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 18.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. TOKYO - DUSK
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Moving over the vast city towards a high rise.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A HELICOPTER thumps into frame, heading for a pad on the roof.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. APARTMENT, TOKYO - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cobb sits, waiting.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Checks his watch, restless.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He pulls a HANDGUN.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Checks it is loaded.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: places it on the table in front of him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Pulls out a PEWTER SPINNING TOP, SPINS it on the table ... He INTENT STUDIES the top's spin... As he stares, the sound of a FREIGHT TRAIN builds and builds- the top WOBBLES, TIPS onto its side- the sound of the train STOPS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: the PHONE RINGS- Cobb GRABS it-
