{DIALOGUE}: Nothing.
{DIALOGUE}: But I can't speak for your friends from Cobol Engineering.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Saito looks out at the city slipping by.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: What do you want from us?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAITO
{DIALOGUE}: Inception.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Arthur raises his eyebrows.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cobb is poker-faced.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAITO
{DIALOGUE}: Is it possible?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARTHUR
{DIALOGUE}: Of course not.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAITO
{DIALOGUE}: If you can steal an idea from someone's mind, why can't you plant one there instead?
