{DIALOGUE}: Okay, here's planting an idea: I say to you, "Don't think about elephants."
{META_DATA}: (MORE)
{DIALOGUE}: 22.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARTHUR (CONT'D)
{META_DATA}: (Saito nods)
{DIALOGUE}: What are you thinking about?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAITO
{DIALOGUE}: Elephants.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARTHUR
{DIALOGUE}: Right.
{DIALOGUE}: But it's not your idea because you know I gave it to you.
