{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 23.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAITO
{DIALOGUE}: Mr. Cobb...?
{DIALOGUE}: There is one other thing I could offer you.
{META_DATA}: (Cobb stops)
{DIALOGUE}: How would you like to go home?
