{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARTHUR
{META_DATA}: (quiet)
{DIALOGUE}: She was lovely.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. ROOFTOP, OLD TOWN, MOMBASA - DAY
