{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sits.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: YUSUF
{DIALOGUE}: You are seeking a chemist?
{META_DATA}: (Cobb nods)
{DIALOGUE}: To formulate compounds for a job?
