{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: We need you there to tailor compounds to our particular requirements.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: YUSUF
{DIALOGUE}: Which are?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: Great depth.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: YUSUF
{DIALOGUE}: A dream within a dream?
{DIALOGUE}: Two levels?
{DIALOGUE}: 51.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: Three.
