{DIALOGUE}: You just have to add a sedative.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: YUSUF
{DIALOGUE}: A powerful sedative.
{DIALOGUE}: How many team members?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: Five.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAITO
{DIALOGUE}: Six.
