{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. MAURICE FISCHER'S INNER OFFICE - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The office is a MAKESHIFT HOSPITAL ROOM: a BED where the desk should be.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Browning addresses a figure at the window.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ROBERT FISCHER, 30'S, abstracted.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BROWNING
{DIALOGUE}: How is he?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Fischer turns to Browning.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Motions silence, as he glances at his FATHER in the bed.
