{CHARACTER_NAME}: FISCHER
{DIALOGUE}: Not now, Uncle Peter.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Browning looks at Fischer, considering.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Biding his time.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: EAMES (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: The vultures are circling.
{DIALOGUE}: The sicker Maurice Fischer becomes, the stronger Peter Browning becomes... 61.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Eames WATCHES Browning, STUDYING his every move .
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. BATHROOM - DAY
