{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. WORKSHOP - CONTINUOUS
{CHARACTER_NAME}: EAMES
{DIALOGUE}: Now, in the dream, I can impersonate Browning and suggest the concepts to Fischer's conscious mind...
{META_DATA}: (draws a diagram)
