{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. YOUNG GIRL'S BEDROOM - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Ariadne pulls back the grill and walks across the room, considering the dusty furnishings.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: At the window is a doll's house, front slightly ajar.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Ariadne opens it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Inside is a SAFE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She tries it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOCKED.
