{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Mal brushes at Cobb's hair, trying to convince him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We hear snatches of conversation-
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MAL
{DIALOGUE}: You remember when you asked me to marry you?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: Of course...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MAL
{DIALOGUE}: You said you had a dream...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: That we'd grow old together.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MAL
{DIALOGUE}: And we can.
