{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: we-
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. WORKSHOP - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Ariadne watches Cobb sleeping.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His eyes gradually flicker open.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He sees her watching him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARIADNE
