{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cobb clears the end of the train, and SKIDS across the tracks-
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Arthur CROUCHES down- PUSHES the accelerator with his HAND- YANKS the wheel- FLYING BLIND.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The cab NAILS the Security Man, CRUNCHING into the front S.U.V.-
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cobb SMASHES his car into the rear S.U.V., creating a GAP-
