{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Looks him in the eye.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: EAMES
{DIALOGUE}: Great.
{DIALOGUE}: So now we're stuck in Fischer's mind battling it out with his private army, and if we get hit we're stuck in Limbo 'til our brains dissolve into scrambled egg?
