{DIALOGUE}: You had no right.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: It's the only way you can go three layers deep, Arthur.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Arthur turns to Yusuf, hostile.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 81.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARTHUR
{DIALOGUE}: And you.
