{DIALOGUE}: 84.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. BATHROOM, WAREHOUSE - MOMENTS LATER
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cobb pushes Browning (Eames), bloody and bruised, into the room and forces him down next to Fischer.
