{DIALOGUE}: "Disappointed."
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Browning can say nothing.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. OFFICE, WAREHOUSE - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cobb pulls off his balaclava.
