{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. HOTEL LOBBY BAR - SUNSET
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Fischer nurses a drink.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Staring at the ice cracking.
