{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. KITCHEN, PENTHOUSE (LIMBO) - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Mal laughs at Cobb.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MAL
{META_DATA}: (laughs)
{DIALOGUE}: Up above?
{DIALOGUE}: Listen to yourself.
{DIALOGUE}: You judged me for believing the very same thing.
