{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SHOCKS Fischer again, and we-
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. PORCH, PENTHOUSE (LIMBO) - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Ariadne looks up as a LARGE BOLT OF LIGHTNING RIPS across the sky... she looks down to see Fischer, BOUND AND BLOODY, lying below the rail.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARIADNE
{DIALOGUE}: He's here.
{DIALOGUE}: And it's time.
{DIALOGUE}: But you have to come with us.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Another massive lightning strike flickers across the sky-
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARIADNE
{DIALOGUE}: Cobb, I'm not going to let you lose yourself in here!
{DIALOGUE}: You have to get back to your children!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: Send Fischer, I have to stay-
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARIADNE
{DIALOGUE}: You can't stay here to be with her-
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cobb turns from Mal.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Looks at Ariadne.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: I'm not.
{DIALOGUE}: Saito is dead by now.
{DIALOGUE}: That means he's here.
{DIALOGUE}: I have to stay here and find him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Ariadne removes Fischer's gag- pulls him up, onto the rail.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cobb looks back at Mal.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: I can't stay here to be with her because she's not real.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Mal looks at Cobb, furious.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MAL
{DIALOGUE}: Not real?
{DIALOGUE}: I'm the only thing you do believe in anymore.
{DIALOGUE}: Here-doesn't this feel real, Dom?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She STABS him in the chest- Cobb WHEEZES- GASPING, looking at Mal- 139.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: I wish you were.
{DIALOGUE}: But I couldn't make you real.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm not capable of imagining you in all your complexity and... perfection.
{DIALOGUE}: As you really were.
{DIALOGUE}: You're the best I can do.
{DIALOGUE}: And you're not real.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Mal pulls the knife and moves to STRIKE again-
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARIADNE
{DIALOGUE}: No!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A SHOT rings out, Mal GRABS her shoulder- Cobb turns to Ariadne, who is pointing Cobb's gun.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COBB
{DIALOGUE}: What're you doing?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARIADNE
{DIALOGUE}: Improvising.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She KICKS Fischer off the roof- AIMS again at Mal-
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Fischer DROPS as the sky LIGHTS UP WITH ELECTRICITY- Fischer SCREAMS, then GASPS, no longer falling, and we are-
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. ANTECHAMBER - DAY
