{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. VAN, UNDERWATER - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Ariadne, Arthur and Yusuf wait calmly underwater.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They are sharing TWO REGULATORS pulled from beneath the front seat.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Arthur turns to Saito.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: There is blood in the water around Saito's belly- his eyes are LIFELESS- Arthur feels for a pulse... turns to Cobb, whose eyes are lifeless... Ariadne GRABS Arthur's elbow, pulling him away...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. RIVERBANK - MOMENTS LATER
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Fischer turns Browning/Eames over.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They lie there, exhausted.
